channel.description:
I have made a loginscreen my way and would like to share it with others. This loginbox should work with Project Insanity, SlashScape, BattleScape Clients. If you want to see how it will look like, a picture is at the end of the thread.
This loginscreen isnt 100%, like there is no hovering, but its still good. Enjoy it if you're going to use.

